gaffer.store.schema

Class StoreElementDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • gaffer.store.schema.StoreElementDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ElementDefinition, Serializable

    public class StoreElementDefinition
extends Object
implements ElementDefinition
    A StoreElementDefinition defines how an Element should be stored in the Store. Specifically this class holds a map of property names to StorePropertyDefinitions.
    See Also:
    StoreElementDefinition.Builder, StoreElementDefinition, Serialized Form
